HEADWORD: Phosphorescent
<hw>Phos`phor*es"cent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>phosphorescent</ets>.]</ety> <def>Shining with a phosphoric light;
emitting phosphorescence; luminous without sensible heat.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A phosphorescent substance.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

